mil.emp3.mapengine.api

Class FeatureVisibility

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.emp3.mapengine.api.FeatureVisibility

  • public class FeatureVisibility
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains a reference to a feature and its visibility. It is used to add or update features on a map instance. If visible is true the feature should be made visible. If its false the feature should not be visible.
